{"id":"1036195343321529812","name":"Bulma Briefs","lastUpdateDate":"2021-10-30T08:42:07.119Z","publisherHandle":"wendelpaulo","publisherImage":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/c532c7cefbe7ae23edf1c7cf113a99c4?size=240&default=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-alpha.figma.com%2Fstatic%2Fuser_w_v2.png","publisherId":"951342383837167060","publisherName":"Wendel Paulo","thumbnailUrl":"https://s3-alpha.figma.com/hub/file/1251749350/9146c188-03ba-4d16-9ab6-72600894583c-cover.png","description":"<p><strong>Bulma Briefs</strong>&nbsp;desempenha o papel de apoio ao protagonista&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Goku\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Goku</a>, no mangá&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Dragon_Ball_(manga)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Dragon Ball</a>&nbsp;e nos animes&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Dragon_Ball_(anime)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Dragon Ball</em></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Dragon_Ball_Z\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Z</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Dragon_Ball_GT\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">GT</a>, e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Dragon_Ball_Super\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Super</a>, filha do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Dr._Brief\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Dr. Brief</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Sra._Brief\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Sra. Brief</a>, ex-namorada de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Yamcha\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Yamcha</a>, mais tarde se torna esposa de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Vegeta\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Vegeta</a>&nbsp;e mãe de seus dois filhos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Trunks\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Trunks</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Bra\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Bra</a>. Bulma é a personagem feminina mais importante da série, sendo responsável por duas invenções relevantes para o anime como o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Radar_do_Drag%C3%A3o\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">radar do dragão</a>&nbsp;e a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/M%C3%A1quina_do_Tempo\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Máquina do Tempo</a>, e tendo participação contínua do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/O_Segredo_das_Esferas_do_Drag%C3%A3o\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">primeiro episódio</a>&nbsp;até o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dragonball.fandom.com/pt-br/wiki/Adeus_Goku..._At%C3%A9_Um_Dia!!!\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">último</a>.</p>","url":"https://www.figma.com/community/file/1036195343321529812"}
